Description: The return of the Holy Family from Egypt accompanied by angels, with Christ pointing to a house before them Engraving
Curator's comments: A considerably modified adaptation (in reverse) of the engraving by Cornelis Galle after G.B.Paggi. For the original see 1949,1008.162
Bibliographic references: Hollstein / Dutch and Flemish etchings, engravings and woodcuts c.1450-1700 (43) (Galle (related to))
Subjects: return of the holy family from egypt
